                    </div>
                    <span>Before I purchased this book I was completely intimidated by the idea of building a Beowulf Cluster. I found this book to be a surprisingly thorough and accessible resource, allowing me to get a great understanding of what was needed. I've just placed my order for the equipment for my first cluster and can't wait to get it up and running!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">I still can't build a beowulf.</div>
